try to please you anymore.

91
00:07:03,060 --> 00:07:04,260
Starting today,

92
00:07:05,380 --> 00:07:07,980
I am no longer Bai Xiyin's shadow.

93
00:07:09,140 --> 00:07:09,740
I

94
00:07:11,700 --> 00:07:13,100
want to be myself.

95
00:07:29,180 --> 00:07:29,980
Why are you...?

96
00:07:31,500 --> 00:07:32,900
How do I look

97
00:07:33,740 --> 00:07:34,540
in this outfit?

98
00:07:36,900 --> 00:07:37,740
I forgot.

99
00:07:38,460 --> 00:07:40,180
You like me in white.

100
00:07:40,300 --> 00:07:41,700
