101
00:07:43,340 --> 00:07:44,020
Since

102
00:07:44,020 --> 00:07:46,060
you've never had romantic feelings
for me,

103
00:07:46,300 --> 00:07:47,980
I shouldn't hold on to you.

104
00:07:48,380 --> 00:07:50,540
Do you have to turn yourself into this?

105
00:07:50,980 --> 00:07:52,340
You are not this kind of person.

106
00:07:52,540 --> 00:07:54,060
This is the real me.

107
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:55,260
I am not her.

108
00:07:55,980 --> 00:07:56,700
Tu Jing.

109
00:08:03,180 --> 00:08:03,620
Why...

110
00:08:04,340 --> 00:08:05,900
Why are you dressed like that today?

111
00:08:07,260 --> 00:08:08,220
Don't you like it?

112
00:08:11,300 --> 00:08:12,100
That's not it.

113
00:08:12,580 --> 00:08:13,900
If you like it,

114
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:16,660
I'll dress like this
every day from now on.

115
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:33,140
Heng.

116
00:08:33,860 --> 00:08:34,620
Have you found

117
00:08:35,180 --> 00:08:36,380
Xieyun?

118
00:08:39,500 --> 00:08:40,300
