121
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:44,300
But

122
00:08:44,900 --> 00:08:45,700
I still haven't found it.

123
00:08:46,260 --> 00:08:47,460
Are you unable to find it,

124
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:49,100
or just don't want to?

125
00:08:50,460 --> 00:08:51,020
Immortal Venerable, please calm down.

126
00:08:51,500 --> 00:08:51,940
I...

127
00:08:57,580 --> 00:08:58,460
Heng.

128
00:08:59,100 --> 00:09:00,660
I'm so disappointed in you!

129
00:09:01,860 --> 00:09:02,700
Immortal Venerable, please calm down.

130
00:09:03,700 --> 00:09:05,380
Please spare Immortal Chen Heng.

131
00:09:05,500 --> 00:09:06,060
He

132
00:09:06,420 --> 00:09:07,940
just wasn't thinking straight.

133
00:09:08,500 --> 00:09:09,300
Heng.

134
00:09:10,100 --> 00:09:12,500
You are the disciple I value most.

135
00:09:14,020 --> 00:09:15,100
Master,

136
00:09:15,260 --> 00:09:16,660
I've let you down.

137
00:09:17,140 --> 00:09:18,980
As an immortal,

138
00:09:19,740 --> 00:09:21,860
your duty is to protect
the Three Realms!

139
00:09:22,580 --> 00:09:23,660
How can you

140
00:09:23,820 --> 00:09:25,860
put the safety of all beings at risk
for personal feelings?

141
00:09:27,100 --> 00:09:27,980
But Xiyin...

142
00:09:27,980 --> 00:09:30,180
I know you share a deep bond with her.

143
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:31,460
But tell me,

144
00:09:32,180 --> 00:09:33,460
who in the Three Realms

145
00:09:33,780 --> 00:09:35,340
doesn't have someone they love?

146
00:09:35,620 --> 00:09:37,460
Are they destined to be lesser than you?

147
00:09:37,940 --> 00:09:39,100
Are their loved ones

148
00:09:39,180 --> 00:09:41,260
to be trampled and sacrificed at will?

149
00:09:44,140 --> 00:09:45,100
Of course not.

150
00:09:45,500 --> 00:09:46,300
Now

151
00:09:46,900 --> 00:09:48,740
she is no longer your junior sister,

152
00:09:49,700 --> 00:09:51,300
but the host of Xieyun.

153
00:09:51,660 --> 00:09:53,660
If Xieyun makes a comeback,

154
00:09:53,980 --> 00:09:54,820
who knows

155
00:09:55,140 --> 00:09:58,100
how many people in the Three Realms
will lose their loved ones.

156
00:10:00,900 --> 00:10:01,740
I

157
00:10:02,260 --> 00:10:03,100
was wrong.

158
00:10:03,700 --> 00:10:05,100
Don't forget your duty

159
00:10:05,860 --> 00:10:06,700
and your position.

160
00:10:08,380 --> 00:10:09,300
Don't let me down

161
00:10:09,860 --> 00:10:11,660
on this again.

162
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:15,140
Understood.

